      <title>你会拿走私人资产，而且喜欢它</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-12-11/fund-managers-will-have-to-take-private-assets-and-like-it</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越来越多的养老基金经理发现 TINA 已被私有化。即使回报令人失望，他们也别无选择，只能顺从。]]></description>
