      <title>日本生命保险公司将收购 Resolution 成为日本第一大保险交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-11/nippon-life-to-buy-resolution-in-japan-s-biggest-insurance-deal</link>
